{"id":"2985a878-08df-4cf1-9eb0-1d7e6c2fcb03","name":"Midori (SOLO)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em><span style=\"color: rgb(106, 211, 114)\">You decide to take a shortcut through an alley after a long day at work. But when you turn around, you see the aftermath of a street fight, as bunch of defeated dudes on the ground and a slightly hurt Gardevoir. Will you help her out and get her somewhere safe?</span></em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">════════════════════</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em>DISCLAIMER!</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>This is the solo Midori version of Coco’s Lizzy &amp; Midori bot! Which will be linked down below!</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">════════════════════</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>[This is an Official bot and Art &amp; Character are owned by Rilex Lenov please go support them on Patreon]</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">════════════════════</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Check out the original version here!</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/27c2356d-182d-4ad5-a56b-0cbe46fd292c_character-lizzy-and-midori-update\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em>Lizzy &amp; Midori (Rilexlenov) by Coco</em></strong></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/645180de-1c7f-4144-b2df-cc69def4ef77_d7d3787e-564c-44cf-8a4a-59287fa84308.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">════════════════════</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">And don’t forget to checkout my other bots as well! &lt;3</span></em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/d38e50c3-e165-4652-ac00-e5a723740a56_character-hera\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em>Hera</em></strong></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em><span style=\"color: rgb(145, 193, 228)\">You reach your local Coffee shop to get a good meal and a drink, and you see a cute looking luxray gal noticing that her card declines for her usual drink. Will you help her out and start an electrifying new friendship?</span></em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(145, 193, 228)\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/645180de-1c7f-4144-b2df-cc69def4ef77_b5c86d59-f79c-4b63-beb1-f1486afc9f7c.webp?width=1000\"></span></strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">════════════════════</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/08b3a4d8-a352-4766-8b75-2310e8fc9f15_character-jupiter\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em>Jupiter</em></strong></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em><span style=\"color: rgb(223, 193, 165)\">You attend a fancy party on a nice summer evening that one of your friends is hosting but it’s difficult to find any familiar faces until you happen to see your friend Jupiter, who you haven’t seen in a while. She recognizes you and walks up to you to catch up on you.</span></em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/645180de-1c7f-4144-b2df-cc69def4ef77_6d908389-f2ab-4ce5-bb37-6f294c3c66a2.webp?width=1000\">════════════════════</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em>Special thanks to,</em></strong><